parameters: Iburu: "Ah... caught up in the commotion... I'm sorry."
Umi: "No! It's Umi! Umi betrayed Kru! That's why this happened!!"
Iburu: "That's not true! It's not like that!"
Iburu: "No good! She's delirious! Please, I beg you, put her to sleep!"
Iburu: "And then... could you remove Kru's memories with hypnosis magic?"

Royal Magician: "It's possible, but... remnants of the memories will
remain."

Iburu: "It can't be helped. Living with the memory of losing a loved one is
harder."
